Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.61,0:00:10.94,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,It appeared as though humanity \Nwould be destroyed by the demons.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.99,0:00:19.16,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,But a single mage saved them all.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.38,0:00:31.46,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,He was called the Wizard King,\Nand he became a legend.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.63,0:00:36.39,main,Messenger,0000,0000,0000,,Th-There's an emergency!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.39,0:00:38.12,main,Messenger,0000,0000,0000,,Th-The capital!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.12,0:00:40.25,main,Messenger,0000,0000,0000,,The capital is under attack!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.09,0:00:48.30,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,The Clover Kingdom fell under attack\Nwhile the Wizard King was absent.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.03,0:00:52.89,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,The royal capital was in flames, \Nand people fled from the dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.97,0:00:58.53,main,Rades,0000,0000,0000,,You're stronger than me, right? Right?!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.53,0:01:01.54,main,Rades,0000,0000,0000,,Get out here, Magic Knights!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.54,0:01:04.62,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,I get it! There are people \Nout there who need our help!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.62,0:01:06.31,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna go!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.31,0:01:07.33,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,Asta!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.33,0:01:08.94,main,Klaus,0000,0000,0000,,Where do you plan to go?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.94,0:01:14.38,main,Klaus,0000,0000,0000,,We don't even know the full situation yet, \Nand you can't sense magic at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.38,0:01:16.13,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to where it's noisiest!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.13,0:01:18.26,main,Klaus,0000,0000,0000,,D-Do you think you're \Nan animal or something?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.09,0:01:21.61,main,Leopold,0000,0000,0000,,Interesting!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.61,0:01:23.89,main,Leopold,0000,0000,0000,,Let's see what you've got!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.89,0:01:26.48,main,Leopold,0000,0000,0000,,Wait for me, Asta, my rival!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.93,0:01:30.98,main,Fuegoleon,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure you'd rather not take orders \Nfrom me, but listen well, Magic Knights!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.31,0:01:33.63,main,Fuegoleon,0000,0000,0000,,I'll go after Leo and that Black Bulls boy,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.63,0:01:35.57,main,Fuegoleon,0000,0000,0000,,and after I've joined them,\Nwe'll head to the north district.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.01,0:01:38.14,main,Fuegoleon,0000,0000,0000,,Silver Eagles, I ask that you \Nhead to the central district,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.14,0:01:40.07,main,Fuegoleon,0000,0000,0000,,where the magic is strongest.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.53,0:01:42.52,main,Fuegoleon,0000,0000,0000,,Blue Roses, head to the east district!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.52,0:01:45.87,main,Charlotte,0000,0000,0000,,I'd rather not take orders from a man, \Nbut I suppose I don't have a choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.37,0:01:50.75,main,Fuegoleon,0000,0000,0000,,Golden Dawn, split into two teams and head \Nto the west and northwest districts!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.75,0:01:52.10,main,Klaus,0000,0000,0000,,Let us go.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.10,0:01:56.01,main,Hamon,0000,0000,0000,,I guess we'll just have \Nto save dessert for later.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.01,0:01:59.48,main,Fuegoleon,0000,0000,0000,,If we fail to protect the royal capital, \Nwe'll bring shame upon the Magic Knights!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.48,0:02:01.26,main,Fuegoleon,0000,0000,0000,,Do not let the enemy escape, no matter what!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.26,0:02:02.76,main,All,0000,0000,0000,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.58,0:02:16.57,main,Rades,0000,0000,0000,,Little girl... Do you \Nlike the Clover Kingdom?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.91,0:02:18.97,main,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,I-I love it!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.58,0:02:23.86,main,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,So please... stop this.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.73,0:02:28.33,main,Rades,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I hate it!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.65,0:02:31.88,main,Rades,0000,0000,0000,,So the town... the people...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.04,0:02:34.80,main,Rades,0000,0000,0000,,And you, too, little girl...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.50,0:02:37.26,main,Rades,0000,0000,0000,,I'll destroy you all!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.30,0:02:41.97,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,The members of the Magic Knights moved out,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.97,0:02:44.35,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,and when Asta arrived...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.19,0:02:51.43,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Then I'll protect them!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.87,0:03:11.75,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,I would always close my eyes
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.75,0:03:16.09,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,And cower at reality
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.09,0:03:20.77,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't stand the idea
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.77,0:03:25.14,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Of just making excuses to give up
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.14,0:03:26.24,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Stand right there
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.24,0:03:27.40,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want to be near you
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.40,0:03:28.54,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Any minute now
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.54,0:03:31.94,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Just wait right there
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.49,0:03:31.94,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,(The decisive battle is still a long way off)
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.94,0:03:34.02,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Black and blue
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.02,0:03:39.94,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll give up on giving up
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.94,0:03:43.45,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,And get the world on my side
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.45,0:03:47.09,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm looking for the reason I'm alive
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.09,0:03:52.33,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Every time somewhere under this sky
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.33,0:03:58.18,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Break through the tearful nights
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.18,0:04:01.47,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,And head where the light shines
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.47,0:04:05.30,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to keep my promise
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.30,0:04:08.85,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll deliver it to you
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.85,0:04:12.82,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,shape of love
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.40,0:04:20.59,Ep Title,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,Wild Magic Dance
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.77,0:04:34.78,main,Man,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.55,0:04:48.55,sign_6799_65_North_District,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,North District
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.98,0:04:56.85,main,Rades,0000,0000,0000,,Someone finally shows up, \Nand it's a Black Bull.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.85,0:04:59.27,main,Rades,0000,0000,0000,,And a little kid to boot.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.58,0:05:02.44,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Get away from her, you crazy bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.44,0:05:09.39,main,Rades,0000,0000,0000,,You fool! You won't be able to stop \Nmy army with that rusty sword!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.54,0:05:13.46,main,Rades,0000,0000,0000,,What...?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.25,0:05:16.62,main,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,I was so scared!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.62,0:05:18.79,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,You really acted fast!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.25,0:05:20.87,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,It's dangerous, so stand back.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.87,0:05:21.84,main,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.84,0:05:26.68,main,Rades,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, I see. You're the one \Nwith the anti-magic.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.68,0:05:28.28,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,You've heard of me?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.28,0:05:31.73,main,Rades,0000,0000,0000,,Man, gimme a break!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.73,0:05:34.67,main,Rades,0000,0000,0000,,No one asked the bottom-ranked Black Bulls
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.67,0:05:38.02,main,Rades,0000,0000,0000,,or a piece of trash like you with no magic
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.02,0:05:40.27,main,Rades,0000,0000,0000,,to show up here!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.26,0:05:48.78,main,Rades,0000,0000,0000,,Do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.78,0:05:55.37,sign_6799_65_North_District,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,Central District
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.37,0:05:58.41,main,Man 2,0000,0000,0000,,Don't think you're going to get away with...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.98,0:06:01.82,main,Man 3,0000,0000,0000,,What? What do you want?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.82,0:06:03.25,main,Man 3,0000,0000,0000,,I'll give it to you, just—
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.46,0:06:11.39,main,People,0000,0000,0000,,It's the Silver Eagles!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.39,0:06:14.39,sign_8905_87_Captain_of_the_S,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,Captain of the Silver Eagles\N{\fs30}Nozel Silva
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.39,0:06:17.77,sign_8905_87_Captain_of_the_S,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,Member of the Silver Eagles\N{\fs30}Solid Silva
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.39,0:06:17.77,top,Man 3,0000,0000,0000,,The Magic Knights have come to save us!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.77,0:06:20.56,top,Man 2,0000,0000,0000,,The captain is here! We're saved!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.77,0:06:21.25,sign_8905_87_Captain_of_the_S,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1,912)}Member of the Silver Eagles\N{\fs30}Nebra Silva
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.56,0:06:23.32,top,Lady,0000,0000,0000,,Lord Nozel! Lord Solid!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.32,0:06:24.90,main,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Lady Nebra!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.90,0:06:27.65,main,Nozel,0000,0000,0000,,Citizens, fall behind us.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.65,0:06:32.66,sign_6799_65_North_District,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,West District
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.10,0:06:39.72,main,Klaus,0000,0000,0000,,What are these things?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.72,0:06:41.69,main,Klaus,0000,0000,0000,,Every time we knock them down,\Nthey get up again!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.01,0:06:49.93,main,Hamon,0000,0000,0000,,I was planning to have dessert when we \Ngot back, but I think I've lost my appetite.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.93,0:06:54.93,sign_6799_65_North_District,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,East District
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.93,0:06:59.00,main,Sol,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa, these things are gross, Sis!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.00,0:07:03.31,main,Charlotte,0000,0000,0000,,Indeed. I feel nauseous just looking at them.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.31,0:07:06.31,main,Charlotte,0000,0000,0000,,Also, be mindful of your tone.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.31,0:07:08.82,main,Sol,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I'll be more careful!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.15,0:07:11.71,main,Charlotte,0000,0000,0000,,Stay away from me!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.32,0:07:17.33,sign_6799_65_North_District,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,Northwest District
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.33,0:07:19.55,main,Mimosa,0000,0000,0000,,There are so many!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.55,0:07:20.95,main,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,Not a chance...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.95,0:07:22.92,main,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,Do they have some kind of weakness?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.83,0:07:28.30,main,Alecdora,0000,0000,0000,,It matters not. There's no point \Nin wasting time trying to find it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.30,0:07:33.30,sign_6799_65_North_District,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,North District
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.30,0:07:35.07,main,noelle,0000,0000,0000,,They're disgusting...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.07,0:07:36.81,main,leopold,0000,0000,0000,,Is my rival safe?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.21,0:07:40.54,main,Fuegoleon,0000,0000,0000,,We can look for the\NBlack Bulls boy later, Leo.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.03,0:07:46.44,main,Fuegoleon,0000,0000,0000,,These things possess magic, \Nbut they aren't alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.89,0:07:47.85,main,Fuegoleon,0000,0000,0000,,In that case...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.69,0:07:51.95,main,All,0000,0000,0000,,We'll just have to crush them \Nuntil they can't get back up!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.95,0:07:54.32,main,Leopold,0000,0000,0000,,See if you can take my magic!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.32,0:07:57.34,main,Leopold,0000,0000,0000,,Flame Magic: Spiral Flames!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.37,0:08:01.21,main,Fuegoleon,0000,0000,0000,,Flame Magic: Sol Linea!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.46,0:08:08.63,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,A-Amazing...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.90,0:08:18.64,main,Klaus,0000,0000,0000,,Steel Creation Magic: Fierce Spiral Lance!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.56,0:08:24.78,main,Hamon,0000,0000,0000,,Goodness, you fight in such a vulgar manner.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.34,0:08:27.53,main,Hamon,0000,0000,0000,,You should at least
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.35,0:08:30.73,main,Hamon,0000,0000,0000,,die in elegance and beauty!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.05,0:08:34.28,main,Hamon,0000,0000,0000,,Glass Creation Magic: Verre Fleur!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.18,0:08:40.98,main,Alecdora,0000,0000,0000,,Shatter before my magic!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.98,0:08:45.12,main,Alecdora,0000,0000,0000,,Sand Creation Magic: \NSand-Armored Heavy Guard!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.42,0:08:51.15,main,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,Wind Magic: Towering Tornado!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.74,0:08:56.55,main,Mimosa,0000,0000,0000,,If you're hurt, please come see me!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.55,0:08:59.56,main,Mimosa,0000,0000,0000,,I will heal you with my \NDream-Healing Flower Cradle.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.52,0:09:03.93,main,Charlotte,0000,0000,0000,,Filthy creatures, stay away from me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.93,0:09:06.81,main,Sol,0000,0000,0000,,Quit grossing my Sis out!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.37,0:09:10.45,main,Sol,0000,0000,0000,,Earth Creation Magic: Raging Mother Goddess!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.74,0:09:16.30,main,Charlotte,0000,0000,0000,,Call me "Captain."
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.08,0:09:27.06,main,Charlotte,0000,0000,0000,,I will not allow anyone to touch me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.87,0:09:32.45,main,Charlotte,0000,0000,0000,,Briar Creation Magic: \NCorpse-Hunting Briar Trees!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.97,0:09:36.52,main,Solid,0000,0000,0000,,You're all eyesores!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.52,0:09:39.97,main,Solid,0000,0000,0000,,Water Creation Magic: Slashing Sea Serpent!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.65,0:09:42.99,main,Nebra,0000,0000,0000,,Mist Magic: Solid Mist Clones!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.75,0:09:53.34,main,Nebra,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, dear. They weren't much fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.86,0:09:59.41,main,Nozel,0000,0000,0000,,Accept your punishment.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.41,0:10:01.99,main,Nozel,0000,0000,0000,,Mercury Magic: Rain of Silver.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.66,0:10:08.33,main,Nozel,0000,0000,0000,,Punishment for the crime of \Ndaring to threaten the people
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.06,0:10:10.21,main,Nozel,0000,0000,0000,,of this country.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.04,0:10:15.17,main,Fuegoleon,0000,0000,0000,,Flame Creation Magic: Leo Rugiens!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.05,0:10:22.43,main,Fuegoleon,0000,0000,0000,,Burn to ashes!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.43,0:10:24.14,main,Man A,0000,0000,0000,,Th-They're amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.14,0:10:25.18,main,Woman A,0000,0000,0000,,The Magic Knights!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.18,0:10:26.57,main,Man B,0000,0000,0000,,They're so powerful!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.57,0:10:28.09,main,Man C,0000,0000,0000,,They're too amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.94,0:10:39.34,main,Leopold,0000,0000,0000,,How'd you like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.11,0:10:42.37,main,Leopold,0000,0000,0000,,That voice!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.38,0:10:47.58,italics,Leopold,0000,0000,0000,,He...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.58,0:10:51.12,italics,Leopold,0000,0000,0000,,Don't tell me he managed to mow down \Nthat many of them with just a sword!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.67,0:10:53.32,italics,Leopold,0000,0000,0000,,He's so strong!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.32,0:10:56.46,italics,Leopold,0000,0000,0000,,What a stupidly straightforward \Nway of fighting!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.61,0:11:01.73,main,Leopold,0000,0000,0000,,He's just too interesting!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.73,0:11:04.82,main,Leopold,0000,0000,0000,,This is why he's my perfect rival!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.38,0:11:12.01,italics,Rades,0000,0000,0000,,My magic runs my own mana through corpses,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.01,0:11:15.02,italics,Rades,0000,0000,0000,,making them move in any way \NI want. It's wraith magic.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.03,0:11:23.45,italics,Rades,0000,0000,0000,,That guy's attacks instantly cut through \Nthe mana in the corpses and erases it!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.85,0:11:28.27,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,I guess that's all of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.27,0:11:30.62,main,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Th-Thank you, mister.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.95,0:11:32.59,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,It's too early to thank me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.35,0:11:38.88,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you attacking \Ninnocent people, you jerk?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.55,0:11:43.18,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to defeat you, no matter what!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.53,0:11:58.94,main,Rades,0000,0000,0000,,Number Four, Jimmy...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.53,0:12:02.45,main,Rades,0000,0000,0000,,"Innocent"?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.45,0:12:05.78,main,Rades,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone who doesn't understand my magic...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.17,0:12:11.61,main,Rades,0000,0000,0000,,is a sinner!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.73,0:12:27.30,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you attacking \Ninnocent people, you jerk?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.97,0:12:31.60,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to defeat you, no matter what!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.89,0:12:47.37,main,Rades,0000,0000,0000,,Number Four, Jimmy...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.91,0:12:50.87,main,Rades,0000,0000,0000,,"Innocent"?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.87,0:12:54.21,main,Rades,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone who doesn't understand my magic...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.55,0:13:00.05,main,Rades,0000,0000,0000,,is a sinner!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.97,0:13:15.25,main,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,They keep coming, one after another...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.25,0:13:18.23,main,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,But they're no match for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.23,0:13:22.15,main,Alecdora,0000,0000,0000,,Just a few more...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.50,0:13:28.78,main,Mimosa,0000,0000,0000,,You're okay now.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.87,0:13:32.58,main,Hamon,0000,0000,0000,,One after another...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.57,0:13:37.50,main,Klaus,0000,0000,0000,,Are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.50,0:13:43.55,main,Hamon,0000,0000,0000,,Goodness, you saved me.\NI'll treat you to some gelato later.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.63,0:13:47.97,main,Sol,0000,0000,0000,,Take that, and that, and that, and that!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.51,0:13:53.27,main,Charlotte,0000,0000,0000,,Every rose has its thorns.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.14,0:13:55.65,main,Nebra,0000,0000,0000,,Mist Spider's Threads.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.06,0:14:01.52,main,Solid,0000,0000,0000,,Water Creation Magic: Holy Water Bullet!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.41,0:14:12.37,main,Rades,0000,0000,0000,,That brat's your prey this time, Jimmy!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.37,0:14:19.54,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! You just keep bringing out these \Ncreepy things one after another!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.54,0:14:21.25,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,No fair, you jerk!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.01,0:14:25.05,italics,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,My wound opened up even more?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.48,0:14:28.82,main,Rades,0000,0000,0000,,Jimmy got you with one of his\Nspecially made curse shells.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.82,0:14:30.89,main,Rades,0000,0000,0000,,It's loaded with curse power.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.30,0:14:34.29,main,Rades,0000,0000,0000,,Even scratches won't stop bleeding.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.29,0:14:36.49,main,Rades,0000,0000,0000,,I'd be real careful if I were you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.49,0:14:37.45,main,Rades,0000,0000,0000,,Jimmy!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.23,0:14:44.44,italics,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,I won't be able to swing \Nmy big sword fast enough!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.99,0:14:50.60,main,Rades,0000,0000,0000,,You sure are a pain for a brat \Nthat doesn't have any magic.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.60,0:14:54.20,main,Rades,0000,0000,0000,,But Jimmy's still got \Nlots of curse power left.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.87,0:15:01.33,main,Rades,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, but before we deal with you...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.11,0:15:07.26,main,Rades,0000,0000,0000,,Jimmy, finish off that eyesore \Nof a brat back there first!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.97,0:15:16.85,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Who are you aiming at?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.85,0:15:22.90,main,Rades,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, right. I guess you Magic Knights\Nprotect the people.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.07,0:15:33.20,main,Rades,0000,0000,0000,,Just abandon her already!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.12,0:15:40.58,main,Rades,0000,0000,0000,,Uh-oh. There's no point in getting hurt \Njust to protect others, is there?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.58,0:15:42.04,main,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Mister...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.51,0:15:47.75,main,Rades,0000,0000,0000,,What do you gain from protecting a little \Nbrat like that, you hypocritical loser?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.91,0:15:52.38,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,I'll protect her, even if I \Ndon't gain anything from it!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.97,0:15:57.17,main,Rades,0000,0000,0000,,Will you? I see. Then stay right there
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.17,0:16:01.69,main,Rades,0000,0000,0000,,and swing your sword around until \Nyou bleed to death, you moron!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.94,0:16:09.82,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,Asta!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.42,0:16:13.20,italics,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,I have to help him.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.20,0:16:22.66,flashback,Solid,0000,0000,0000,,You can't even control your magic. \NYou're such an embarrassment.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.08,0:16:26.81,flashback,Nebra,0000,0000,0000,,You've basically been exiled \Nfrom the Silva family.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.81,0:16:30.26,flashback,Nebra,0000,0000,0000,,I'm surprised you had the nerve \Nto return to the Noble Realm.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.04,0:16:33.76,flashback,Nozel,0000,0000,0000,,You do not belong here.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.10,0:16:35.14,flashback,Nozel,0000,0000,0000,,Begone,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.27,0:16:38.73,flashback,Nozel,0000,0000,0000,,failure that killed our mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.61,0:16:42.11,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,I-I can't... Someone...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.78,0:16:45.69,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,Someone... Please, someone help Asta...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.00,0:16:59.83,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,Thank y—
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.83,0:17:02.83,main,Fuegoleon,0000,0000,0000,,Focus!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.83,0:17:06.83,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,Ow! What was that for?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.21,0:17:08.74,main,Fuegoleon,0000,0000,0000,,Black Bulls girl,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.07,0:17:13.47,main,Fuegoleon,0000,0000,0000,,you're not letting what your \Nsiblings said get to you, are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.38,0:17:18.26,main,Fuegoleon,0000,0000,0000,,There's no time for that on the battlefield!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.49,0:17:22.55,main,Fuegoleon,0000,0000,0000,,One wrong decision and a life could be lost!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.85,0:17:28.73,main,Fuegoleon,0000,0000,0000,,You're standing here right now \Nas a member of the Magic Knights!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.09,0:17:32.93,main,Fuegoleon,0000,0000,0000,,If you joined the Magic Knights \Nof your own free will,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.37,0:17:35.67,main,Fuegoleon,0000,0000,0000,,then steel yourself and get stronger!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.67,0:17:37.20,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,Steel myself?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.73,0:17:39.87,main,Fuegoleon,0000,0000,0000,,Being weak is nothing to be ashamed of.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.99,0:17:43.87,main,Fuegoleon,0000,0000,0000,,However, staying weak is!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.61,0:17:48.05,italics,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,He's right...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.15,0:17:52.10,italics,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,He's the one who proved that to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.34,0:17:57.31,italics,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,If he can do it, I can also...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.59,0:18:03.10,italics,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,become stronger!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.37,0:18:09.78,main,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Mister!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.02,0:18:17.19,main,Rades,0000,0000,0000,,The weak will always die weak!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.66,0:18:25.50,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Crap!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.30,0:18:27.46,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,I won't make it in time!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.51,0:18:39.71,main,Rades,0000,0000,0000,,Who the hell are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.71,0:18:40.84,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Noelle!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.84,0:18:43.10,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing, Stupidsta?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.50,0:18:45.46,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,I can't bear to just sit and watch this.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.46,0:18:48.44,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,I'll help you, so you'd better be grateful!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.44,0:18:49.27,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Got it!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.64,0:18:52.47,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,There's no way he can stop \Nyou if you can move freely.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.47,0:18:53.58,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,Go!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.57,0:18:56.44,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like you're back to normal.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.44,0:18:58.86,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,I was never feeling down!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.86,0:19:00.91,main,Rades,0000,0000,0000,,You stupid brats!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.49,0:19:06.87,main,Rades,0000,0000,0000,,Don't get so full of yourselves!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.83,0:19:14.66,main,Leopold,0000,0000,0000,,I shall assist you, my rival!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.66,0:19:20.22,main,Leopold,0000,0000,0000,,Get that bastard good! \NShow me your true power!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.69,0:19:24.14,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Uh... Thank you very much!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.14,0:19:25.85,main,Leopold,0000,0000,0000,,There's no need to thank me!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.85,0:19:30.55,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,And I was going to do that anyway!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.14,0:19:48.12,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Not yet! I'm not done yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.86,0:19:53.12,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Whoops...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.13,0:19:57.34,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,You did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.34,0:19:58.96,main,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Mister!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.96,0:20:04.42,main,Leopold,0000,0000,0000,,You don't fight like any other mage!\NYou're just too interesting!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.98,0:20:12.62,main,Rades,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.62,0:20:17.69,main,Rades,0000,0000,0000,,Don't let that ridiculous \Nattack get to you, Jimmy!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.11,0:20:19.66,main,Rades,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Jimmy!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.66,0:20:21.24,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Stop blabbering.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.61,0:20:24.24,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Come at me yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.24,0:20:29.94,main,Rades,0000,0000,0000,,Wha? Don't get cocky, you little brat!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.07,0:20:33.10,main,Rades,0000,0000,0000,,Come forth, Alfred.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.65,0:20:43.76,main,Rades,0000,0000,0000,,Number Two, Alfred.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.26,0:20:48.71,main,Rades,0000,0000,0000,,Go, Alfred!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.58,0:21:11.58,main,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,Asta...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.22,0:21:37.60,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,My dry emotions gaze at the me from that day
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.60,0:21:40.57,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,And push me forward
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.57,0:21:42.61,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,(I can't find a place to go)
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.61,0:21:47.89,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Even the faintest light can \Nstill break through the darkness
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.89,0:21:53.39,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,And change the flow of time
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.12,0:21:55.81,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,(I will keep believing in you)
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.81,0:21:58.69,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,In this ever-vivid place
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.69,0:22:01.63,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,(Break free yourself)
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.63,0:22:04.53,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,In order to grasp my endless dream
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.53,0:22:07.19,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,If there is a path that I should choose
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.19,0:22:09.25,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,(Do you wanna try? Do you wanna try?)
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.25,0:22:12.16,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Wherever it may lead us
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.16,0:22:14.65,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Until my life comes to an end
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.65,0:22:17.33,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,I will accept any pain that comes my way
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.33,0:22:19.35,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,(We can try again, we can try again)
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.35,0:22:23.71,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if we can't see tomorrow
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.71,0:22:29.26,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Holding onto feelings too intense to voice
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.82,0:22:32.99,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll keep screaming them in my heart
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.88,0:22:48.34,sign_33083_276_Petit_Clover_,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1,520)}Pe{\c&H3BC020&}t{\c&HE2AF0F&}i{\c&H3BC020&}t C{\c&HE2AF0F&}l{\c&H3BC020&}o{\c&H0E42D4&}ve{\c&H3BC020&}r
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.78,0:22:47.34,main,All,0000,0000,0000,,Petit Clover!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.11,0:22:51.84,sign_33188_278_The_Mystery_of_t,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(520,1)}Ra
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.69,0:22:49.50,main,Rades,0000,0000,0000,,Ra!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.84,0:22:53.17,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.17,0:22:54.41,main,Rades,0000,0000,0000,,Hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.41,0:22:56.18,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Asta. Nice to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.60,0:23:00.11,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,So, you haven't actually said \Nyour name in the show yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.11,0:23:02.19,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Could you tell us what it is?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.19,0:23:04.94,main,Rades,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, my name is Rades.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.19,0:23:04.94,italicstop,Rades,0000,0000,0000,,(Hai, ore no namae wa Radesu desu.)
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.94,0:23:07.45,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Radesdes? I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.45,0:23:09.70,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,So where did you come from, Radesdes?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.70,0:23:12.94,main,Rades,0000,0000,0000,,No, it's not Radesdes. \NYou don't need the "des."
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.94,0:23:15.84,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,We don't need the des? \NSo your name is just Ra?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.84,0:23:16.97,main,Rades,0000,0000,0000,,Who're you calling Ra?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.97,0:23:18.52,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Well, you said there was no "des."
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.52,0:23:21.50,main,Rades,0000,0000,0000,,It's Rades! I just mean \Nyou don't need the "des."
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.50,0:23:23.46,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,It's Radesdes, but you don't need the "des"...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.46,0:23:26.15,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,So if you take out all the "des,"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.15,0:23:27.10,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,It's just Ra?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.74,0:23:32.51,main,Rades,0000,0000,0000,,I'm telling you that's not right!\NI'm Rades! Rades!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.51,0:23:37.99,main,Rades,0000,0000,0000,,You better remember that, you useless brats!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.53,0:23:43.02,main,Rades,0000,0000,0000,,The Magic Knights are no match for me!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.02,0:23:45.77,main,Rades,0000,0000,0000,,I, Rades, am the strongest of them all!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.19,0:23:50.86,main,rades,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Black Clover{\i0}, Page 23:\N"The Crimson Lion King."
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.44,0:23:55.00,sign_34238_338_Page_2_The_Boys_,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(234,1)}Page 23\N\N{\fs18} The Crimson Lion King
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.86,0:23:53.74,main,Rades,0000,0000,0000,,Controlling corpses is my magic!
